messages.message:
Feedback on sample apps, forgive me if you’ve already seen this feedback
• Passport app not loading sample files “Error loading” 
• DL app doesn’t extract gender from 2/3 sample DLs (even though it is present on doc)
• Payslip app
    ◦ 289 shows gross and net the same, although information for deductions is present
    ◦ 308 does not show gross pay although all necessary information for the math is there
    ◦ 339 gross pay is wildly incorrect
@avi and @debstuti.das can we take a look at these things? the sample files loading issue is being fixed

And I think my followup question on this is, if the user finds that the apps are not working correctly for them, is there any way they can iterate on them at this point? Or would they just need to start from scratch in Build?
which environment were you testing the apps in @jean?
I’m in the internal launch, so yeah, https://aihub.instabase.com/
Thanks so much for the feedback. For the payslip app, we are planning to remove the gross pay field, on driver's licence, we'll look into it
